### Stonecutter (multi-version build) — generated per-version subprojects + preprocessor cache ###
versions/
.stonecutter/

### Modpack mod jars — downloaded deps + built skyseed jar (tracked via each pack's mods.txt manifest) ###
**/overrides/mods/*.jar

### Downloaded + runtime-generated shader/resource packs — not committed (listed in mods.txt). Keep the empty folders via .gitkeep. ###
**/overrides/shaderpacks/*
!**/overrides/shaderpacks/.gitkeep
**/overrides/resourcepacks/*
!**/overrides/resourcepacks/.gitkeep

### Machine-specific / per-instance marker & cache configs — so the whole overrides/config/ folder can be copied in as-is without hand-removing these. ###
**/overrides/config/embeddium-fingerprint.json
**/overrides/config/xaeropatreon.txt
**/overrides/config/euphoria_patcher/.data.json
**/overrides/config/etf_warnings.json

### Auto-generated config regenerated on first launch (derived from the installed mod set, not curated pack config) ###
# JEI mod/type/category ordering — auto-appended as mods are added; regenerates identically.
**/overrides/config/jei/*-sort-order.ini
# Sound Physics per-sound rate table — 1700+ auto-generated default entries (occlusion/reflectivity/soundphysics.properties ARE kept).
**/overrides/config/sound_physics_remastered/sound_rates.properties
# Editor/mod backup files.
*.bak
